OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,FEngland have reached the semi-finals
OL,7,Fof the World Cup, facing Argentina for
OL,8,Fthe first time since 2005.
OL,10,FIt's fair to say there is a lot of
OL,11,Fhistory between the two sides. Here's
OL,12,Fwhat we know as the old rivalry is
OL,13,Frenewed.
OL,15,FWhere and when do the semi-finals take
OL,16,Fplace?
OL,18,FEngland play Argentina at the Mercedes-
OL,19,FBenz Stadium in Atlanta, Georgia on
OL,20,FWednesday at 8pm UK time. The game
OL,21,Fwill be aired live by the BBC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,FITV will air the other semi-final,
OL,7,FFrance vs Spain, which is at 8pm UK
OL,8,Ftime on Tuesday at the Dallas Stadium
OL,9,Fin Arlington, Texas.
OL,11,FCould weather affect the game?
OL,13,FThundery showers are predicted for
OL,14,FWednesday in Atlanta. Normally this
OL,15,Fwould risk triggering FIFA's
OL,16,Fthunderstorm protocol, but the
OL,17,FMercedes-Benz Stadium has a
OL,18,Fretractable roof so the game will not
OL,19,Fbe impacted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
