OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,FThe high on Wednesday is currently
OL,7,Fexpected to be 30C. However, the
OL,8,Fstadium has powerful air-conditioning
OL,9,Fand state of the art climate control.
OL,11,FWhat's the history between the two
OL,12,Fsides?
OL,14,FEngland have played Argentina in five
OL,15,Fprevious World Cup tournaments:
OL,17,F1962: England beat Argentina 3-1 in
OL,18,Fthe group stages, but there was little
OL,19,Fcontroversy around the game.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
