OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,F1966: This is when the rivalry between
OL,7,Fthe two sides and their fans really
OL,8,Fgot started. England beat Argentina 1-
OL,9,F0 in the quarter-final, a game
OL,10,Freferred to in Argentina as "el robo
OL,11,Fdel siglo" (the theft of the century).
OL,12,FThey claimed that the winning goal by
OL,13,Fstriker Geoff Hurst was offside.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
