OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,FThe match was the first encounter
OL,7,Fbetween the two sides since the war in
OL,8,Fthe Falklands.
OL,10,F1998: England's round of 16 clash with
OL,11,FArgentina is remembered for 23-year-
OL,12,Fold David Beckham, then one of
OL,13,FEngland's brightest stars, receiving a
OL,14,Fred card.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
