PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,F2002: Beckham was England captain by
OL,7,Fthe time the two teams met at another
OL,8,FWorld Cup, this time in the group
OL,9,Fstages. He redeemed himself by scoring
OL,10,Fthe only goal of the game from the
OL,11,Fpenalty spot, in a 1-0 win for England.
OL,13,FAlthough Argentina disputed the
OL,14,Fawarding of a penalty, for a foul on
OL,15,FMichael Owen by Mauricio Pochettino,
OL,16,Fthe game was relatively good-spirited.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
