OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,FFriendly 2005: The teams have not
OL,7,Fplayed each other for more than 20
OL,8,Fyears. Their last meeting was a
OL,9,Ffriendly in 2005, which saw England
OL,10,Fcome twice from behind to beat
OL,11,FArgentina 3`2.
OL,13,FWhat do the stats say?
OL,15,FReigning champions Argentina have
OL,16,Flifted the World Cup trophy three
OL,17,Ftimes - in 1978, 1986 and 2022.
OL,19,F1966 was the first, and famously the
OL,20,Flast, time England has won the
OL,21,Ftournament.....to date.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
