OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,FAs we head into the semi-finals,
OL,7,FArgentina top of FIFA's World Cup goal
OL,8,Frankings, having scored 17 times in
OL,9,Fthis tournament. England are fourth,
OL,10,Fwith 13 goals.
OL,12,FHowever, when it comes to conceding,
OL,13,Fthe teams are are level at 6 goals
OL,14,Feach.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
