OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,FIn the race for Golden Boot,
OL,7,FArgentina's Lionel Messi is second
OL,8,Fonly to France's Kylian Mbappe. They
OL,9,Fhave both scored 8 goals so far in
OL,10,Fthis tournament, but Mbappe is ranked
OL,11,Ftop because he has played fewer
OL,12,Fminutes.
OL,14,FNorway's Erling Haaland remains in
OL,15,Fthird place, with 7 goals, but Jude
OL,16,FBellingham and Harry Kane are only one
OL,17,Fbehind him with 6 goals each.
OL,18,FBellingham is ranked ahead of Kane,
OL,19,Fagain because of time spent on the
OL,20,Fpitch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
