OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,FWhat has England said about Argentina ?
OL,8,FThomas Tuchel says there is "nowhere
OL,9,Felse in the whole wide world" he would
OL,10,Frather be than leading England into a
OL,11,FWorld Cup semi-final against reigning
OL,12,Fchampions Argentina.
OL,14,FHowever, there is precious little time
OL,15,Fto prepare to face Lionel Messi and co
OL,16,Fat the majestic Mercedes-Benz Stadium.
OL,18,FEngland flew straight back from
OL,19,FSaturday's clash in Miami to Kansas
OL,20,FCity, where Argentina are also based.
