OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,F"The next three days are crucial, of
OL,7,Fcourse, to be ready," the England boss
OL,8,Fsaid. "We have another flight, but
OL,9,Fthis victory will help a lot, this
OL,10,Ffeeling will help a lot.
OL,12,FWhat has Argentina said about England?
OL,14,FArgentina Manager Lionel Scaloni
OL,15,Fsought to put politics aside after his
OL,16,Fteam beat Switzerland to go through to
OL,17,Fthe semi-final against England.
OL,19,F"Look, this is a football game," he
OL,20,Fsaid. "OK, so the message is this is a
OL,21,Ffootball game. That's what I can say.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
