PN,31314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,F"It is a football game and we will be
OL,7,Fplaying against a very tough opponent.
OL,8,FThey have an excellent coach and this
OL,9,Fis a football game and that's all."
OL,11,FCaptain Lionel Messi, who has never
OL,12,Fplayed against England, said the
OL,13,Fmeeting would be "special".
OL,15,FAlthough 39-year-old Messi wasn't even
OL,16,Fborn in 1986, he was asked about that
OL,17,Flegendary encounter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
