PN,31315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783921779
OL,3,CA rivalry renewed: England's semi-
OL,4,Cfinal clash with Argentina
OL,6,F"Everything I have seen and remember
OL,7,Fis from videos and images that
OL,8,FArgentinians constantly watch and
OL,9,Frelive," he told sports channel ESPN
OL,10,FArgentina.
OL,12,F"Obviously, playing against England is
OL,13,Fspecial because they are a powerhouse,
OL,14,Fand matches against powerhouses are
OL,15,Falways special. Personally, it's the
OL,16,Ffirst time I'm going to play against
OL,17,Fthem. I've played against everyone
OL,18,Fexcept England, so it will be nice for
OL,19,Fthat reason too."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
